">\n                        Tighten and improve texture for healthy, revitalized skin.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"text-xs text-stone-600 space-y-2 mb-6 border-t border-stone-100 pt-4\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> Opus Plasma</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> CO2 Laser</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> RF Microneedling</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> Laser Hair Removal</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <a href=\"#booking\" class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-stone-900 group-hover:text-[#E3C15E] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1\">\n                        Book Now <iconify-icon icon=\"solar:arrow-right-linear\"></iconify-icon>\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Card 4: Body Wellness -->\n                <div class=\"group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-stone-100 flex flex-col\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-[#D1DDE8]/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-stone-700 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">\n                        <iconify-icon icon=\"solar:body-linear\" width=\"24\"></iconify-icon>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3\">Body Wellness</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow\">\n                        Revitalize and energize for a healthier body inside and out.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"text-xs text-stone-600 space-y-2 mb-6 border-t border-stone-100 pt-4\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> IV Drip Infusions</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> Hair Restoration</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><iconify-icon icon=\"solar:check-circle-linear\" class=\"text-[#E3C15E]\"></iconify-icon> Wellness Support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <a href=\"#booking\" class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-stone-900 group-hover:text-[#E3C15E] transition-colors flex items-center gap-1\">\n                        Book Now <iconify-icon icon=\"solar:arrow-right-linear\"></iconify-icon>\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Booking / New Patients -->\n    <section id=\"booking\" class=\"py-24 bg-white relative\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6\">\n            <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 border border-stone-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\">\n                <!-- Form Side -->\n                <div class=\"lg:col-span-3 p-8 lg:p-16 bg-white\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-10\">\n                        <span class=\"text-[#E3C15E] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2 block\">New Patient?</span>\n                        <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-medium text-stone-900\">Request Appointment</h2>\n                        <p class=\"text-stone-500 text-sm mt-3\">Fill out the form below and our team will contact you to confirm.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <form id=\"appointment-form\" onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault()