er payment plans. Please note most cosmetic procedures are not covered by insurance.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Footer -->\n    <footer class=\"bg-[#2C2C2C] text-stone-300 pt-20 pb-10 text-sm font-light\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6\">\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-stone-700\">\n                <div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-serif text-white mb-6\">Cloud La Med Spa</h2>\n                    <p class=\"max-w-xs text-stone-400 mb-6\">\n                        Blending medical expertise with artistic vision to help you look and feel your best.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-4\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cloud_la_medspa/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-700 hover:bg-[#E3C15E] text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"mdi:instagram\" width=\"20\"></iconify-icon>\n                        </a>\n                        <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cloudlamedspa\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-700 hover:bg-[#E3C15E] text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"mdi:facebook\" width=\"20\"></iconify-icon>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-6\">Quick Links</h3>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n                        <li><a href=\"#services\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Cosmetic Injectables</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#services\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Skin Rejuvenation</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#services\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Body Wellness</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#team\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">About Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-6\">Legal</h3>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-3\">\n                        <li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Accessibility</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-stone-500\">\n                <p>© 2026 Cloud La Med Spa. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n                <p>Designed with care for New Jersey.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <!-- Location Modal Script & Mobile Menu Script -->\n    <script>\n        // Mobile Menu Toggle\n        const btn = document.getElementById('mobile-menu-btn');\n        const overlay = document.getElementById('mobile-menu-overlay');\n        const content = document.getElementById('mobile-menu-content');\n        const close = document.getElementById('mobile-menu-close');\n        const links = document.querySelectorAll('.mobile-link');\n\n        function toggleMenu() {\n            const isHidden = overlay.classList.contains('opacity-0');\n            \n            if (isHidden) {\n                // Open\n                overlay.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'pointer-events-none');\n                overlay.classList.add('opacity-100', 'pointer-events-auto');\n                content.classList.remove('translate-x-full');\n                content.classList.add('translate-x-0');\n            } else {\n                // Close\n                overlay.classList.remove('opacity-100', 'pointer-events-auto');\n                overlay.classList.add('opacity-0', 'pointer-events-none');\n                content.classList.remove('translate-x-0');\n                content.classList.add('translate-x-full');\n            }\n        }\n\n        btn.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);\n        close.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);\n        overlay.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n            if(e.target === overlay) toggleMenu();\n        });\n        \n        // Close menu when a link is clicked\n        links.forEach(link => {\n            link.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body></html>","language":"html","username":"f68fe5b4-2b12-4cec-8b86-7b689a8ddd9e","created_at":"2026-06-08T08:56:57.679757+00:00","views":717,"image_url":"https://hoirqrkdgbmvpwutwuwj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preview-images/medical-spa-landing-30.png?t=1781071381691","forks":19,"private":false,"watermark":true,"featured":true,"share_source_code":true,"user_id":"f68fe5b4-2b12-4cec-8b86-7b689a8ddd9e","category":"Mobile","updated_at":null,"tags":["Health","Services","Clean","Minimal","Professional","Wellness","Medical","Beauty"],"description":"A high-end, brand-forward landing page template designed for medical spas, wellness clinics, and aesthetic practitioners to showcase services and book appointments.","premium":false,"price":null,"purchase_url":null,"long_description":"## Elevate Your Aesthetic Practice\n\nThis premium **Medical Aesthetics & Wellness Template** is meticulously designed to project luxury and trust for high-end clinics. It features a refined color palette of brand gold and blue-grey, perfectly suited for the health and beauty industry.\n\n### Key Features\n- **Comprehensive Service Hub:** Categorized sections for injectables, skin rejuvenation, resurfacing, and body wellness.\n- **Conversion-Optimized Hero:** High-impact visual sections with clear primary and secondary CTAs to drive bookings.\n- **Professional Trust Signals:** Dedicated trust strip for board certifications, awards, and reviews to build immediate credibility.\n- **Integrated Booking Form:** A modern appointment request system designed specifically for new patients.\n- **Fully Responsive Navigation:** Includes a sticky header and a mobile-optimized menu for seamless cross-device browsing.\n\n### Primary Use Case\nIdeal for **medical professionals**, **dermatologists**, and **wellness entrepreneurs** looking to establish a sophisticated digital presence that converts visitors into patients.","custom_domain":null,"favicon_light_url":null,"favicon_dark_url":null,"dns_verified":null,"dns_verified_at":null,"dns_a_record":null,"netlify_apex_exists":null,"netlify_www_exists":null,"netlify_verified_at":null,"custom_domain_added_at":null,"netlify_site_id":null,"umami_website_id":null,"umami_share_id":null,"analytics_enabled":false,"gtm_container_id":null,"remix_source":{"url": "https://aura.build/templates/cloudlamedspanj", "slug": "cloudlamedspanj", "title": "Medical Spa Landing Page Template", "authorName": "CrazeCatch", "authorSlug": "user-1b460d80", "sharedCodeId": "17693", "sharedReactProjectId": null},"credit_remix_source":true,"search_visibility":"aura_and_custom_domain","llms_txt":null,"llms_txt_updated_at":null}]